{
    "name": "Default",
    "settings": "{\"settings\":\"{\\n    \\\"[csharp]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"csharpier.csharpier-vscode\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[css][scss][less]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"vscode.css-language-features\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[dockercompose]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.autoIndent\\\": \\\"advanced\\\",\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"redhat.vscode-yaml\\\",\\n        \\\"editor.insertSpaces\\\": true,\\n        \\\"editor.quickSuggestions\\\": {\\n            \\\"comments\\\": false,\\n            \\\"other\\\": true,\\n            \\\"strings\\\": true\\n        },\\n        \\\"editor.tabSize\\\": 2\\n    },\\n    \\\"[github-actions-workflow]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"redhat.vscode-yaml\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[html]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"vscode.html-language-features\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[javascript][javascriptreact][typescript]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"vscode.typescript-language-features\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[json][jsonc]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"vscode.json-language-features\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[markdown]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"yzhang.markdown-all-in-one\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[nginx]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"raynigon.nginx-formatter\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[python]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"ms-python.black-formatter\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[shellscript]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"foxundermoon.shell-format\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"[sql]\\\": {\\n        \\\"editor.defaultFormatter\\\": \\\"mtxr.sqltools\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"accessibility.underlineLinks\\\": true,\\n    \\\"autoalign.minSeparationLeft\\\": 2,\\n    \\\"autoalign.moveableItemsAdditional\\\": [\\n        \\\"#\\\",\\n        \\\"AS\\\",\\n        \\\"from\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"chat.agentFilesLocations\\\": {\\n        \\\".agents/agents\\\": true\\n    },\\n    \\\"chat.instructionsFilesLocations\\\": {\\n        \\\".github/instructions\\\": true,\\n        \\\".claude/rules\\\": true,\\n        \\\"~/.copilot/instructions\\\": true,\\n        \\\"~/.claude/rules\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-collections-post-response.instructions.md\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-collections-pre-request.instructions.md\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-folder-post-response.instructions.md\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-folder-pre-request.instructions.md\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-http-request-post-response.instructions.md\\\": true,\\n        \\\"/var/folders/py/8cfc8wls159bp1p4dkr6q7bm0000gn/T/postman-http-request-pre-request.instructions.md\\\": true\\n    },\\n    \\\"chat.mcp.gallery.enabled\\\": true,\\n    \\\"chat.promptFilesLocations\\\": {\\n        \\\".agents/prompts\\\": true\\n    },\\n    \\\"chat.tools.terminal.enableAutoApprove\\\": false,\\n    \\\"chat.viewSessions.orientation\\\": \\\"stacked\\\",\\n    \\\"diffEditor.codeLens\\\": true,\\n    \\\"diffEditor.ignoreTrimWhitespace\\\": false,\\n    \\\"editor.accessibilitySupport\\\": \\\"off\\\",\\n    \\\"editor.bracketPairColorization.independentColorPoolPerBracketType\\\": true,\\n    \\\"editor.cursorSmoothCaretAnimation\\\": \\\"on\\\",\\n    \\\"editor.detectIndentation\\\": true,\\n    \\\"editor.fontFamily\\\": \\\"FiraCode Nerd Font Mono\\\",\\n    \\\"editor.fontSize\\\": 13,\\n    \\\"editor.insertSpaces\\\": true,\\n    \\\"editor.minimap.enabled\\\": false,\\n    \\\"editor.suggestSelection\\\": \\\"first\\\",\\n    \\\"editor.tabSize\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"editor.unicodeHighlight.ambiguousCharacters\\\": false,\\n    \\\"emmet.includeLanguages\\\": {\\n        \\\"csv\\\": \\\"html\\\",\\n        \\\"javascript\\\": \\\"javascriptreact\\\",\\n        \\\"json\\\": \\\"html\\\",\\n        \\\"jsonc\\\": \\\"html\\\",\\n        \\\"plaintext\\\": \\\"html\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"explorer.fileNesting.patterns\\\": {\\n        \\\"*.db\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.db3\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.js\\\": \\\"${capture}.js.map, ${capture}.min.js, ${capture}.d.ts\\\",\\n        \\\"*.jsx\\\": \\\"${capture}.js\\\",\\n        \\\"*.s3db\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.sdb\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.sqlite\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.sqlite3\\\": \\\"${capture}.${extname}-*\\\",\\n        \\\"*.ts\\\": \\\"${capture}.js\\\",\\n        \\\"*.tsx\\\": \\\"${capture}.ts\\\",\\n        \\\"package.json\\\": \\\"package-lock.json, yarn.lock, pnpm-lock.yaml, bun.lockb, bun.lock\\\",\\n        \\\"tsconfig.json\\\": \\\"tsconfig.*.json\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"files.autoSave\\\": \\\"afterDelay\\\",\\n    \\\"files.exclude\\\": {\\n        \\\"**/.classpath\\\": true,\\n        \\\"**/.factorypath\\\": true,\\n        \\\"**/.project\\\": true,\\n        \\\"**/.settings\\\": true\\n    },\\n    \\\"files.simpleDialog.enable\\\": true,\\n    \\\"files.watcherExclude\\\": {\\n        \\\"*.log\\\": true\\n    },\\n    \\\"git.autofetch\\\": true,\\n    \\\"git.openRepositoryInParentFolders\\\": \\\"never\\\",\\n    \\\"git.replaceTagsWhenPull\\\": true,\\n    \\\"github.copilot.chat.copilotMemory.enabled\\\": true,\\n    \\\"github.copilot.enable\\\": {\\n        \\\"*\\\": true,\\n        \\\"markdown\\\": false,\\n        \\\"plaintext\\\": false,\\n        \\\"scminput\\\": false\\n    },\\n    \\\"javascript.preferences.renameMatchingJsxTags\\\": true,\\n    \\\"liveServer.settings.donotShowInfoMsg\\\": true,\\n    \\\"liveServer.settings.donotVerifyTags\\\": true,\\n    \\\"markdown-preview-enhanced.breakOnSingleNewLine\\\": false,\\n    \\\"markdownlint.config\\\": {\\n        \\\"MD010\\\": false,\\n        \\\"MD033\\\": false,\\n        \\\"MD036\\\": false\\n    },\\n    \\\"peacock.affectEditorGroupBorder\\\": true,\\n    \\\"peacock.affectPanelBorder\\\": true,\\n    \\\"peacock.affectSideBarBorder\\\": true,\\n    \\\"peacock.elementAdjustments\\\": {\\n        \\\"activityBar\\\": \\\"lighten\\\",\\n        \\\"statusBar\\\": \\\"none\\\",\\n        \\\"titleBar\\\": \\\"none\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"peacock.favoriteColors\\\": [\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Blue II\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#29ADFF\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Blue\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#1D2B53\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Brown\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#AB5236\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Green\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#003923\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Orange\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FFA300\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Peach\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FFCCAA\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Pink II\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FF77A8\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Pink\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#7E2553\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Purple\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#83769C\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Red\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FF004D\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"White\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FFF1E8\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n            \\\"name\\\": \\\"Yellow\\\",\\n            \\\"value\\\": \\\"#FFEC27\\\"\\n        }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"peacock.keepBadgeColor\\\": true,\\n    \\\"peacock.surpriseMeFromFavoritesOnly\\\": true,\\n    \\\"peacock.surpriseMeOnStartup\\\": true,\\n    \\\"redhat.telemetry.enabled\\\": false,\\n    \\\"search.useGlobalIgnoreFiles\\\": true,\\n    \\\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.osx\\\": \\\"zsh\\\",\\n    \\\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows\\\": \\\"Git Bash\\\",\\n    \\\"terminal.integrated.fontFamily\\\": \\\"FiraCode Nerd Font Mono\\\",\\n    \\\"timing.clipboard.writingEnabled\\\": true,\\n    \\\"timing.hoverTimestamp.targetFormat\\\": [\\n        \\\"YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ss\\\",\\n        \\\"dddd, DD MMM YYYY HH:mm:ss\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"timing.insertConvertedTime\\\": false,\\n    \\\"todo-tree.general.tags\\\": [\\n        \\\"ASSUME\\\",\\n        \\\"BUG\\\",\\n        \\\"FEATURE\\\",\\n        \\\"FIXME\\\",\\n        \\\"TODO\\\",\\n        \\\"XXX\\\",\\n        \\\"[ ]\\\",\\n        \\\"[x]\\\",\\n        \\\"assume\\\",\\n        \\\"bug\\\",\\n        \\\"fixme\\\",\\n        \\\"hack\\\",\\n        \\\"todo\\\",\\n        \\\"xxx\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"typescript.preferences.renameMatchingJsxTags\\\": true,\\n    \\\"typescript.tsserver.log\\\": \\\"verbose\\\",\\n    \\\"window.commandCenter\\\": false,\\n    \\\"window.customTitleBarVisibility\\\": \\\"auto\\\",\\n    \\\"window.newWindowProfile\\\": \\\"Default\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.activityBar.location\\\": \\\"bottom\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.browser.openLocalhostLinks\\\": true,\\n    \\\"workbench.editor.editorActionsLocation\\\": \\\"titleBar\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.iconTheme\\\": \\\"material-icon-theme\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.preferredHighContrastColorTheme\\\": \\\"Default Dark Modern\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.secondarySideBar.defaultVisibility\\\": \\\"hidden\\\",\\n    \\\"workbench.sideBar.location\\\": \\\"right\\\",\\n    \\\"zenMode.showTabs\\\": \\\"none\\\"\\n}\"}",
    "keybindings": "{\"keybindings\":\"// Place your key bindings in this file to override the defaults\\n[\\n    { \\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+n\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"explorer.newFile\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"explorerViewletFocus\\\" \\n    },\\n    { \\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+shift+n\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"explorer.newFolder\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"explorerViewletFocus\\\" \\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+shift+1\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.openEditorAtIndex1\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorTextFocus\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+shift+9\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.lastEditorInGroup\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorTextFocus\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"shift+cmd+g\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"-editor.action.previousMatchFindAction\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorFocus\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"shift+cmd+g\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.view.scm\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"workbench.scm.active\\\"\\n    },\\n\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"ctrl+shift+cmd+b\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.tasks.runTask\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+shift+b\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"-workbench.action.tasks.build\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"taskCommandsRegistered\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"alt+c\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"markdown.extension.checkTaskList\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorTextFocus && !editorReadonly && editorLangId == 'markdown' || editorTextFocus && !editorReadonly && editorLangId == 'rmd'\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"alt+s\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"markdown.extension.editing.toggleStrikethrough\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorTextFocus && !editorReadonly && editorLangId == 'markdown' || editorTextFocus && !editorReadonly && editorLangId == 'rmd'\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"ctrl+shift+cmd+[\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.moveEditorLeftInGroup\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+k shift+cmd+left\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"-workbench.action.moveEditorLeftInGroup\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"ctrl+shift+cmd+]\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.moveEditorRightInGroup\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+k shift+cmd+right\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"-workbench.action.moveEditorRightInGroup\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"cmd+k cmd+o\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"workbench.action.files.openFolder\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"ctrl+shift+space\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"editor.action.triggerSuggest\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorHasCompletionItemProvider && textInputFocus && !editorReadonly && !suggestWidgetVisible\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"ctrl+space\\\",\\n      \\\"command\\\": \\\"-editor.action.triggerSuggest\\\",\\n      \\\"when\\\": \\\"editorHasCompletionItemProvider && textInputFocus && !editorReadonly && !suggestWidgetVisible\\\"\\n    }\\n]\",\"platform\":1}",
    "tasks": "{\"tasks\":\"{\\r\\n    // See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=733558\\r\\n    // for the documentation about the tasks.json format\\r\\n    \\\"version\\\": \\\"2.0.0\\\",\\r\\n    \\\"tasks\\\": [\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"echo\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"echo Hello\\\"\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"Node: Current\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"node '${file}'\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"python: Current\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"python '${file}'\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"bash: Current\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"bash '${file}'\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"git: archive\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"git archive master -o output.zip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"7z: archive\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"7z a archive.zip ${fileDirname}\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"7z: list all files\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"7z l archive.zip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"7z: extract\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"7z x archive.zip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"tar: archive\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"tar -cf archive.zip ${fileDirname}\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"tar: list all files\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"tar -tf archive.zip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"tar: extract\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"tar -xf archive.zip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"ngrok\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"ngrok http \\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"Java Run\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"./gradlew run\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"python: Generate Cookie\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"python -c \\\\\\\"import os,base64; print(base64.urlsafe_b64encode(os.urandom(32)).decode())\\\\\\\" | clip\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"bash: Generate Cookie\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"dd if=/dev/urandom bs=32 count=1 2>/dev/null | base64 | tr -d -- '\\\\n' | tr -- '+/' '-_'; echo\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"bash: Encode Base64\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"echo 'Hello, World' | base64\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"bash: Decode Base64\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"echo 'Hello, World' | base64 -d\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"ssh: Generate Key Pair\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 2048 -f neix-key.pem\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"ssh: Access Server With Key\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"ssh -i neix-key.pem ubuntu@54.173.100.10\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"ssh: Copy SSH Key to remote Server\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"ssh-copy-id -i neix-key.pem.pub ubuntu@54.173.100.10\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        {\\r\\n            \\\"label\\\": \\\"bash: Run 'Daily Backup'\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"shell\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"java -jar 'C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\E138807\\\\\\\\Documents\\\\\\\\daily-backup.jar'\\\",\\r\\n            \\\"problemMatcher\\\": []\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    ]\\r\\n}\"}",
    "snippets": "{\"snippets\":{\"ansible.json\":\"{\\n\\t\\\"Starter\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"playbook\\\", \\\"starter\\\", \\\"init\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"---\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${playbook_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  hosts: ${host_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  gather_facts: True\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  become: False\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  vars: []\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  roles: \\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  tasks: \\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Starter Playbook\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Ansible Copy Snippet\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"copy_directory\\\", \\\"copy_file\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  copy:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    src: ${2:/path/to/source}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    dest: ${3:/path/to/destination}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Ansible Copy Snippet\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Delete File Or Directory\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"delete_file\\\", \\\"delete_directory\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  file:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file_or_directory}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: absent\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Delete Or Remove Directory\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Create Directory\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"create_directory\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  file:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/directory}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: directory\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Create New Directory\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Change File or Folder Permission\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"chmod\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  file:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    mode: '0755'\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Change File or Directory Permission\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Create New File\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"create_file\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  file:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/myfile.txt}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: touch\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Create New File\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"CURL Url\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"curl\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  uri:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    url: ${2:url}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    return_content: yes\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  register: ${3:debug_variable}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${4:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  debug:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    var: ${3:debug_variable}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"CURL Url\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Unzip file\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"unzip\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  unarchive:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    src: ${2:/path/to/source}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    dest: ${3:/path/to/destination}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Unzip File\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Debug List of Running Process\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"ps\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  shell: ps aux | grep ${2:process_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  register: process_list\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- debug:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    var: process_list.stdout\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Debug list of running process\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Check Service Status\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"systemctl\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  service:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    - name: ${2:service_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: started\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Check Service Status\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Set Cron Job\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"cron\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  cron:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    - name: ${2:service_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    minute: \\\\\\\"0\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    hour: \\\\\\\"2\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    job: ${3:\\\\\\\"/path/to/command\\\\\\\"}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Set Cron Job\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Install Software\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"install_software\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  apt:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    name: ${1:file_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: latest\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Install Software\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Search-And-replace file in line\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"lineinfile\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  lineinfile:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file.txt}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    line: \\\\\\\"${3:Line To Replace}\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    insertafter: \\\\\\\"${4:^Pattern to match}\\\\\\\"\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Search and replace line in file\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Create template\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"template\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  template:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    src: ${2:/path/to/source}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    dest: ${3:/path/to/destination}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Create New Template\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Run Shell Command\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": [\\\"shell\\\", \\\"run_file\\\"],\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  shell: ${2:shell_command}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  register: ${3:variable}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${4:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  debug:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    var: ${3:variable}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Run Shell Command\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Debug Variable\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"debug\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  debug:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    var: ${2:variable}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Debug Variable\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Include Playbook from other file\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"include_tasks\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- include_tasks: ${1:/path/to/playbook.yml}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  tags:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    - ${2:playbook_term}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Include Playbook from other file\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Ansible If Else\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"when_block\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  when: ${2:cond_name}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  block:\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Ansible if else\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Ansible Handlers\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"handlers\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"handlers:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${2:handle_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  systemd:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: restarted\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    name: ${3:service_name}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Ansible Handlers\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Ansible Looping\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"loop\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:task_description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  copy:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    src: \\\\\\\"/answers/{{item.name}}\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    dest: \\\\\\\"/var/www/html_{{item.env}}/index.html\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  loop:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  - { env: 'dev', name: 'dev_index.html'}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  - { env: 'test', name: 'test_index.html'}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  - { env: 'qa', name: 'qa_index.html'}\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Ansible Looping\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Import Tasks\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"import_tasks\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": \\\"- import_tasks: ${1:/path/to/source}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Import Tasks\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Search-And-Replace II\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"lineinfile\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:Task Description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  lineinfile:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file.txt}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    regexp: \\\\\\\"${3:^Pattern to match}\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    line: \\\\\\\"${4:Line To Replace}\\\\\\\"\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Search-And-Replace II\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Insert New Line\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"insert\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:Task Description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  lineinfile:\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file.txt}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    line: \\\\\\\"${3:Line To Replace}\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: present\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    create: true\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Insert New Line\\\"\\n\\t},\\n\\t\\\"Remove Line\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"remove\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"- name: ${1:Task Description}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"  lineinfile:  \\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    path: ${2:/path/to/file.txt}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    regexp: \\\\\\\"${3:^Pattern to match}\\\\\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    state: absent\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Remove Line\\\"\\n\\t}\\n}\",\"aspnetcorerazor.json\":\"{}\",\"cmake.json\":\"{\\n\\t// Place your snippets for cmake here. Each snippet is defined under a snippet name and has a prefix, body and \\n\\t// description. The prefix is what is used to trigger the snippet and the body will be expanded and inserted. Possible variables are:\\n\\t// $1, $2 for tab stops, $0 for the final cursor position, and ${1:label}, ${2:another} for placeholders. Placeholders with the \\n\\t// same ids are connected.\\n\\t// Example:\\n\\t// \\\"Print to console\\\": {\\n\\t// \\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"log\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"console.log('$1');\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"$2\\\"\\n\\t// \\t],\\n\\t// \\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Log output to console\\\"\\n\\t// },\\n\\t\\\"CMakeLists\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"cmake\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.10)\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"# set the project name\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"project($proj_name)\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"# add the executable\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"add_executable(\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    $proj_name main.cpp\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\")\\\"\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Generate Boilerplate for CMake Lists\\\"\\n\\t}\\n}\",\"cpp.json\":\"{\\n\\t// Place your snippets for cpp here. Each snippet is defined under a snippet name and has a prefix, body and \\n\\t// description. The prefix is what is used to trigger the snippet and the body will be expanded and inserted. Possible variables are:\\n\\t// $1, $2 for tab stops, $0 for the final cursor position, and ${1:label}, ${2:another} for placeholders. Placeholders with the \\n\\t// same ids are connected.\\n\\t// Example:\\n\\t// \\\"Print to console\\\": {\\n\\t// \\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"log\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"console.log('$1');\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"$2\\\"\\n\\t// \\t],\\n\\t// \\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Log output to console\\\"\\n\\t// },\\n\\t\\\"Cpp Main Function\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"cpp\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"#include <iostream>\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"using namespace std;\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"int main() {\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    cout << \\\\\\\"$1\\\\\\\" << endl;\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"    return 0;\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"}\\\",\\n\\t\\t],\\n\\t\\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Generate Main Program Layout\\\"\\n\\t}\\n}\",\"csharp.json\":\"{\\n\\t// Place your snippets for csharp here. Each snippet is defined under a snippet name and has a prefix, body and \\n\\t// description. The prefix is what is used to trigger the snippet and the body will be expanded and inserted. Possible variables are:\\n\\t// $1, $2 for tab stops, $0 for the final cursor position, and ${1:label}, ${2:another} for placeholders. Placeholders with the \\n\\t// same ids are connected.\\n\\t// Example:\\n\\t// \\\"Print to console\\\": {\\n\\t// \\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"log\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"console.log('$1');\\\",\\n\\t// \\t\\t\\\"$2\\\"\\n\\t// \\t],\\n\\t// \\t\\\"description\\\": \\\"Log output to console\\\"\\n\\t// }\\n\\t\\\"Http Get Controller\\\": {\\n\\t\\t\\\"prefix\\\": \\\"httpGet\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\\"body\\\": [\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"[HttpGet()]\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"[Route(\\\\\\\"${1:funcName}\\\\\\\")]\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"public HttpResponseMessage ${1:funcName}([FromBody] JToken postData)\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"{\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\tstring Result = \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\";\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\tstring ResponseCode = clsConst.const_ResponseCode_SystemError;\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\tJObject jobj = new JObject();\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\ttry\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t{\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tstring Messaging = postData.ToString();\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t// Log FileName\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tclsLogger.InfoLog(\\\\\\\"${2:projName} ${1:funcName}\\\\\\\");\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tclsLogger.InfoLog(Messaging);\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t// Parameters\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tJObject paramObj = clsFuncs.GenJObj(Messaging);\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t${3:// params}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tbool flag = false;\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t// Condition\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t${4:// condition}\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\tif (flag)\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t{\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\t\\\"\\\\t\\\\t\\\\tRes